OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in fatal collision
OL,6,FTributes have been made to a teenage
OL,7,Fboy who died following a fatal
OL,8,Fcollision in Swansea on Thursday 9
OL,9,FJuly.
OL,11,FThe family of Ceiran Evans described
OL,12,Fhim as having "a kind heart" and said
OL,13,Fhe will always be remembered.
OL,15,FIt comes after police were called to
OL,16,FPen Cae Crwn Road, Gorseinon in
OL,17,FSwansea at around 1pm on Thursday 9
OL,18,FJuly following a report of a collision
OL,19,Finvolving a car and an off-road bike.
