OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784053123
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in fatal collision
OL,6,FThe family of Ceiran Evans has issued
OL,7,Fthe following tribute: "Ceiran was
OL,8,Floved more than any words can say and
OL,9,Fwill be missed every single day. His
OL,10,Fkind heart, wicked sense of humour,
OL,11,Floving nature, and handsome smile
OL,12,Fbrought so much joy to everyone who
OL,13,Fknew him.
OL,15,F"He will forever be our precious baby
OL,16,Fboy; always loved, always remembered,
OL,17,Fand never forgotten."
OL,19,FTyler Ford, 18, from Morriston has
OL,20,Fbeen charged with the murder of Ceiran
OL,21,FEvans, following the incident.
OL,26,@oD@XOUyD@UO]
