OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F439A1784053123
OL,3,CFamily pay tribute to teenager who
OL,4,Cdied in fatal collision
OL,6,FFord has also been charged with
OL,7,Fattempted murder of a second victim.
OL,9,FFour other men who were arrested as
OL,10,Fpart of the investigation are on
OL,11,Fpolice bail.
OL,13,FDet Ch Insp Thorne said: "We are aware
OL,14,Fof social media footage circulating
OL,15,Ffrom this incident, and we once again
OL,16,Fask that this is not shared for
OL,17,Fobvious reasons."
OL,19,FSouth Wales Police have said any
OL,20,Fwitnesses or people with video footage
OL,21,Fof the incident should contact them.
